  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Rat Dog Reality:</strong> A very focused rat dog just trying to break into higher planes of existence.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chaotic Levels:</strong> Explore 15 bizarre stages, each built around a completely different gameplay style, mood, and ruleset. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wild Soundscapes:</strong> Chris Parrello and Lobby Hotel deliver an eclectic, reality-bending soundtrack that mutates with every floor.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Replayable Ridiculousness:</strong> Everything inside is high-scorable. Please speedrun this game. I'm begging.</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506080/extras/3b97b370b262eea757af007f92bbbb8e.poster.avif?t=1765472936\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506080/extras/3b97b370b262eea757af007f92bbbb8e.webm?t=1765472936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506080/extras/3b97b370b262eea757af007f92bbbb8e.mp4?t=1765472936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Descend through absurd layers of history as a rat-dog-witch trying to escape employment and transcend reality. Explore weird museums, cosmic hallways, and your own bad dreams in a chaotic mash-up of art, humor, and a playable existential crisis.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506080/extras/7780ea109641f04470e609778f6be442.poster.avif?t=1765472936\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506080/extras/7780ea109641f04470e609778f6be442.webm?t=1765472936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506080/extras/7780ea109641f04470e609778f6be442.mp4?t=1765472936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fuzz Dungeon invites players into an evolving funhouse of human absurdity. Enter into a playable collage of forgotten centuries, workplace dread, and divine nonsense. Each floor feels like a fever dream of culture itself, only it's been put through a broken xerox machine and dunked in a concoction of strange chemicals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506080/extras/0927ab0c9654732641862f45b5aaf20d.poster.avif?t=1765472936\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506080/extras/0927ab0c9654732641862f45b5aaf20d.webm?t=1765472936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506080/extras/0927ab0c9654732641862f45b5aaf20d.mp4?t=1765472936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The deeper you go, the more the systems collapse-- time becomes malleable, enemies become jokes, and your inventory fills with objects that shouldn’t exist. But you're not just exploring the dungeon; you're travelling through an absurdist version of human history.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506080/extras/8cae77a901b239317ffb87c05d6bfc8d.poster.avif?t=1765472936\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506080/extras/8cae77a901b239317ffb87c05d6bfc8d.webm?t=1765472936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506080/extras/8cae77a901b239317ffb87c05d6bfc8d.mp4?t=1765472936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Funny, sad, and endlessly strange, Fuzz Dungeon is a pilgrimage through the chaos of creation. A game about getting lost, laughing about it, and realizing the exit might just be the punchline.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506080/extras/3b97b370b262eea757af007f92bbbb8e.poster.avif?t=1765472936\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506080/extras/3b97b370b262eea757af007f92bbbb8e.webm?t=1765472936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506080/extras/3b97b370b262eea757af007f92bbbb8e.mp4?t=1765472936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Descend through absurd layers of history as a rat-dog-witch trying to escape employment and transcend reality. Explore weird museums, cosmic hallways, and your own bad dreams in a chaotic mash-up of art, humor, and a playable existential crisis.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506080/extras/7780ea109641f04470e609778f6be442.poster.avif?t=1765472936\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506080/extras/7780ea109641f04470e609778f6be442.webm?t=1765472936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506080/extras/7780ea109641f04470e609778f6be442.mp4?t=1765472936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fuzz Dungeon invites players into an evolving funhouse of human absurdity. Enter into a playable collage of forgotten centuries, workplace dread, and divine nonsense. Each floor feels like a fever dream of culture itself, only it's been put through a broken xerox machine and dunked in a concoction of strange chemicals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506080/extras/0927ab0c9654732641862f45b5aaf20d.poster.avif?t=1765472936\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506080/extras/0927ab0c9654732641862f45b5aaf20d.webm?t=1765472936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506080/extras/0927ab0c9654732641862f45b5aaf20d.mp4?t=1765472936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The deeper you go, the more the systems collapse-- time becomes malleable, enemies become jokes, and your inventory fills with objects that shouldn’t exist. But you're not just exploring the dungeon; you're travelling through an absurdist version of human history.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506080/extras/8cae77a901b239317ffb87c05d6bfc8d.poster.avif?t=1765472936\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506080/extras/8cae77a901b239317ffb87c05d6bfc8d.webm?t=1765472936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506080/extras/8cae77a901b239317ffb87c05d6bfc8d.mp4?t=1765472936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Funny, sad, and endlessly strange, Fuzz Dungeon is a pilgrimage through the chaos of creation. A game about getting lost, laughing about it, and realizing the exit might just be the punchline.</p>",
